    <!-- Dialogs -->
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Ready.Title">Ready to Apply Changes</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Ready.Msg">The selected software and tweaks will now be applied to your system.&#x0a;&#x0a;Ensure you have saved your work as some operations may restart system components.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Ready.Confirm">Start Setup</sys:String>
    
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Safety.Title">System Protection</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Safety.Msg">It is highly recommended to create a system restore point before applying these changes. This ensures you have a safety net if anything behaves unexpectedly.&#x0a;&#x0a;Would you like to create a restore point now? (Takes ~30 seconds)</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Safety.Confirm">Create Point</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Safety.Skip">Skip</sys:String>

    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Modded.Title">Modded Software Warning</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Modded.Msg">You are selecting a modded version of this software. Modded software is not official and may contain community patches or modifications.&#x0a;&#x0a;WinZ is not liable for any issues arising from the use of modded software. Do you wish to continue?</sys:String>

    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Cancel.Title">Cancel Setup</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.Cancel.Msg">Are you sure you want to cancel? This will stop current operations and attempt to revert changes.</sys:String>

    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.ModdedExp.Title">Experimental Features</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.ModdedExp.Msg">Enabling [modded software] allows you to install community-patched versions of applications. These versions may include premium features or community modifications.&#x0a;&#x0a;Modded items will appear with a [subtle blue background] in the list.&#x0a;&#x0a;**Warning:** Security and stability are not guaranteed. Proceed at your own risk.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.ModdedExp.Confirm">Enable</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="L.Diag.ModdedExp.Cancel">Go Back</sys:String>

